<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrī jayābhyudaya śālivāhana śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1440 Agunēṁṭi bahudhānya saṁvvatsara Ā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṣāḍa śu 12 Ā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmatu puṣpagiri sdhitāśēṣa vidvanmahājanālunnugoṁṭūri mummaḍi reḍḍi koḍu 
<lb n="3"/>ku mummaḍireḍki yicinaśāsanaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> māgoṁṭūru cernnuri saṁddu polamēra va<unclear>ra</unclear>ku Ayīvuṁḍaṁgā 
<lb n="4"/>nu nīvu polamēra pārijēyiṁccinaṁdukunēmu peṭina polamēra mānyaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kaḍamarla vāṁgukuvu 
<lb n="5"/>ttara polamēranu cēnu khaṁ<unclear>cēnuṁnnu</unclear> yaṟaguḍi kāluva nērēṭi kāluva vuttamu gaṁḍa kāluva <unclear>lō</unclear>nu 
<lb n="6"/>maḍi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> maḍinni Āceṁdrārkkasdhāyigānu Anabhaviṁcuvāṁḍavu Iṁduku yavvaru tapi nānu paṁcchamahāpātakā 
<lb n="7"/>laṁbōṁgalavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> maṁgaḷamahā śrī śrīṁcēyunu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

